{"tid":858210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：中國改造網絡插頭　讓黑客入侵美國電訊網絡","createTime":"2018-10-11T15:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T07:30:53.000Z","uid":66943,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fde3b31a4d77862d446f0e7bd36f43866e6f1c05","tid":858210,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"繼早前彭博（Bloomberg）發表報告，指中國曾令硬件生產商在主機板加裝具黑客功能的晶片後，最近又再發表另一份相關報告。報告指有資訊保安專家在美國一間大型電訊公司裡面，發現伺服器中的網絡插口被改造，黑客可透過後門入侵電訊公司的電腦網絡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/43531072_359393928131656_5475547681323483136_n-694x391.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F43531072_359393928131656_5475547681323483136_n-694x391.png&h=01d3661f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《彭博》報道，一間與美國主要電訊公司合作的資訊保安專家 Yossi Appleboum，發現伺服器的網絡插口被物理改造。網絡插口是電腦主機板與網路線連接的電腦零件。該名保安專家指，此改造容許黑客透過後門進入電訊公司的電腦網絡。專家未能確認甚麼類型的數據曾通過受感染的伺服器。該電訊公司的伺服器，多為早前報道疑被植入間諜晶片的 Super Micro 所生產。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-10-10-18.37.34-694x410.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-10-10-18.37.34-694x410.png&h=0402ee2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資訊保安專家 Yossi Appleboum 指出，他曾看過不少硬件進口商所使用的中國零件有被改造的情況，並不單止 Super Micro 發生問題。他擔心的是，中國產業鏈內無數地方可被操控，在大部份情況下，要杜絕有關情況出現是不可能的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2018-10-10-18.27.26-694x491.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2018-10-10-18.27.26-694x491.png&h=161199cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲彭博今次列出消息來源，是來自一名受聘於電訊公司的資訊安全專家 Yossi Appleboum<br />\n<br />\n在《彭博》第一篇有關伺服器主機板被中國植入間諜晶片的報道，被外界批評內容提及的資料來源皆由匿名人士提供，缺乏可信性。在最新報道中，由於保安專家 Yossi Appleboum 與電訊公司簽署了保密協議，《彭博》同樣未能報道是哪一間主要電訊公司，受到這些改造網絡插口的影響。"},{"pid":"6840fc09dbffa28b54aa7a39f7534ecc31a9e265","tid":858210,"uid":4168,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"呢啲嘢中共真係領先全球"},{"pid":"34a5e02bbcaa30ccd3050f55b913e7e9318e2e3a","tid":858210,"uid":156611,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:18:17.000Z","msg":"幾時都話其實中國人資質唔差<br />\n但係要唔走正路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4617528c110ca518d957b8fa9d075185df8c3de4","tid":858210,"uid":30633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"全球杯葛"},{"pid":"9025d69a7f0c0cd2d19494b2d1d4769194ba58b8","tid":858210,"uid":163954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"點解得晶片做唔到？"},{"pid":"26a193a907e29e6e0af857d3ec3d2e68eae566d2","tid":858210,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"442ea4466caeae035dfc1ac5639195096bfc0a5b","tid":858210,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf2aeea3ca6eef0d4b87cad14d166a1f9195d4d","tid":858210,"uid":106233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"勁啊"},{"pid":"50fee0a1dba1c805e1a7d0dd3a20f06a74906b79","tid":858210,"uid":47027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9025d69a7f0c0cd2d19494b2d1d4769194ba58b8","tid":858210,"uid":163954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"點解得晶片做唔到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T17:21:09.000Z","msg":"係制程落後，90nm可以自主研發架㗎，不過人哋廿年前嘅科